    <description>V.I.P.E.R. or The Official Handbook of the Venerable Institute of Practitioners of Extraplanetary Racing (which is quite a mouthful by any standard).  The game is a basic space racing game with a free form construction and movement system, similar in concept to things like Full Thrust and Car Wars where there is a large amount of work to be undertaken before the game is actually playable.  The game comes with a die and counters for ships and marker buoys but could easily be played with spaceship miniatures.  As with Car Wars, the game has both a race component and a &amp;quot;blow the opponent out of the sky&amp;quot; component.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
